      <section eId="sec_400_20">
        <num>400.20</num>
        <heading>Waiting period in connection with the sale or transfer of a rifle or shotgun</heading>
        <subsection eId="sec_400_20__subsec_a">
          <num>(a)</num>
          <content>
            <p>NICS has issued\na "proceed" response to the seller or transferor, or</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
        <subsection eId="sec_400_20__subsec_b">
          <num>(b)</num>
          <content>
            <p>thirty calendar\ndays shall have elapsed since the date the seller or transferor\ncontacted NICS to initiate a national instant criminal background check\nand NICS has not notified the seller or transferor that the transfer of\nthe rifle or shotgun to such person should be denied.\n</p>
          </content>
        </subsection>
      </section>
